headline: Western Digital to Announce First Quarter Fiscal Year 2026 Financial Results on October 30, 2025
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., October 14, 2025--Western Digital Corp. (Nasdaq: WDC), the backbone of the AI-driven data economy, plans to announce its first quarter fiscal year 2026 financial results after the market closes on Thursday, October 30, 2025. The company will host a conference call with the investment community to discuss these results on October 30, 2025, at 1:30 p.m. Pacific / 4:30 p.m. Eastern. A live audio webcast and a webcast replay of the conference call will be available at investor.wdc.
